        "q": "How does the balance work?",
        "a": "The aineron.ru balance is in rubles. Each message to an AI model costs a few rubles (usually 1–5 ₽). Funds do not expire, balance is topped up via Robokassa without commission."
      },
      {
        "q": "Is a VPN required to use the service?",
        "a": "No. aineron.ru is a Russian service with servers in Russia. Accessible without VPN, payment with Russian cards, works in any browser and app."
      },
      {
        "q": "Which AI models are available?",
        "a": "Available models include GPT-4o, GPT-4o mini, Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Gemini 1.5 Pro, DeepSeek V3, Mistral, Llama, and over 200 others. For images: Stable Diffusion, Flux, Midjourney-compatible models."
      },
      {
        "q": "Is there an API for developers?",
        "a": "Yes. The API is compatible with OpenAI SDK — just change the base_url and API key. Works with Cursor, VS Code (Continue), GitHub Copilot alternatives, and any OpenAI-compatible app."
      },
      {
        "q": "How to make a payment?",
        "a": "Via Robokassa: Visa/MasterCard/Mir cards, YooMoney, SBP. Balance top-up for any amount and discounted subscriptions available. For legal entities — invoice and contract."
      },
      {
        "q": "What if the AI gives a poor response?",
        "a": "Each message has a 'Regenerate' button — the AI will generate a new response without additional charge. If a technical error occurs, funds are automatically refunded."
